                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">--Over 1,000 pages of in-depth technical content for the most popular web technologies, for only $19.99. <BR>--This book covers ASP, ADO and XML, the most essential technologies used for web programming on the Windows platform. <BR>--Web programmers learn how to use ASP, ADO and XML together to build complex, dynamic web sites that support e-commerce. </span>
              
